<metadata><idinfo><citation><citeinfo><title>5FT_Contours_Stateplane</title><geoform>vector digital data</geoform></citeinfo></citation><descript><abstract>This dataset represents Contours with an 5 foot interval as derived with 1 meter elevation data that was collected and compiled under the auspices of the 3DEP, This data was acquired from USGS The National Map using the 1M National Elevation Dataset Tiles that were derived from the aformentioned elevation data collection projects. The contours are in a state plane coordinate system with all elevations values in feet. The input 1 meter Digital Elevation Model data was converted from meters to feet and then smoothed in a 9 X 9 grid to produce a more cartographically pleasing output.</abstract><purpose>Statewide 5 Foot contours produced by the Arkansas GIS Office using the USGS 1 Meter National Elevation Dataset tiles and other elevation datasets. Dataset is tiled using the input data time framework.</purpose></descript><keywords><theme><themekt>None</themekt><themekey>Contours</themekey><themekey>5 ft</themekey></theme><theme><themekey>Contours</themekey><themekey>5 ft</themekey><themekey>elevation</themekey></theme></keywords><accconst>None</accconst><useconst>None</useconst><datacred>Arkansas GIS Office, USGS</datacred><native>Microsoft Windows 7 Version 6.1 (Build 7601) Service Pack 1; Esri ArcGIS 10.6.0.8321</native></idinfo><spdoinfo><direct>Vector</direct><ptvctinf><sdtsterm><sdtstype>String</sdtstype><ptvctcnt>0</ptvctcnt></sdtsterm></ptvctinf></spdoinfo><spref><horizsys><planar><mapproj><mapprojn>NAD 1983 StatePlane Arkansas North FIPS 0301 Feet</mapprojn><lambertc><stdparll>34.93333333333333</stdparll><stdparll>36.23333333333333</stdparll><longcm>-92.0</longcm><latprjo>34.33333333333334</latprjo><feast>1312333.333333333</feast><fnorth>0.0</fnorth></lambertc></mapproj><planci><plance>coordinate pair</plance><coordrep><absres>0.000000027453728179693832</absres><ordres>0.000000027453728179693832</ordres></coo